subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Turkey postponed on Monday the start of its soccer season by five weeks, until Sept. 9, because of a match-fixing investigation that has landed 30 suspects in jail, including the president of the league champion, Fenerbahce.
